{"tid":1568662,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[Twitter戰線] 5毛一定用呢條片係咁洗版 要快D拆","createTime":"2019-09-14T10:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:57:36.000Z","uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6778e0428ce6276e2f3854308323e8130e3001","tid":1568662,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"[有片][精彩回顧] 天水圍打柒藍絲廢老<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eaCpGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eaCpGS</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇之前既一張圖同片可以解釋到之前藍絲亂打人<br />\n之後示威者先去幫手既片 要用呢招拆<br />\n好似當時831果陣 Twitter 5毛係咁用示威者地鐵同呀伯打 <br />\n係之後有人用佢拎鐵錘既圖先解到 <br />\n不過都有唔少外國左膠信左佢地<br />\n要快D啦"},{"pid":"9dd7eb73ccf1261de978af074678771a83ebc197","tid":1568662,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span> <br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccFUCqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccFUCqw.jpg&h=f44c3870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b381b94bdcd6f3b0bec2b0db8b63f25b32c2ec74","tid":1568662,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56e46c18bcfa392e4dc6d7dced673a071bbcfa21","tid":1568662,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfc5866a6d14d0e2e0f0f598557f45c217397755","tid":1